<h:html xmlns:h="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:orx="http://openrosa.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2002/xforms" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:jr="http://openrosa.org/javarosa">
	<h:head>
		<h:title>Seguimento</h:title>
		<model>
			<instance>
				<data xmlns:jrm="http://dev.commcarehq.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://openrosa.org/formdesigner/d2401a55c30432c0881f8a2f7eaa179338253051" uiVersion="1" version="504" name="Seguimento">
					<home_visit/>
					<referral_status/>
					<health_status_followup/>
					<status_unknown/>
					<other_comments/>
					<educ_same_worse/>
					<educ_importance_hf/>
					<referral_form/>
					<new_registration/>
					<educ_better/>
					<educ_followup_again/>
					<prev_referral_given/>
					<new_referral_given/>
					<close_case/>
				<case xmlns="http://commcarehq.org/case/transaction/v2" case_id="" user_id="" date_modified=""><update><referral_given/></update><close/></case><orx:meta xmlns:cc="http://commcarehq.org/xforms"><orx:deviceID/><orx:timeStart/><orx:timeEnd/><orx:username/><orx:userID/><orx:instanceID/><cc:appVersion/></orx:meta></data>
			</instance><instance src="jr://instance/session" id="commcaresession"/><instance src="jr://instance/casedb" id="casedb"/>
			<bind nodeset="/data/home_visit"/>
			<bind nodeset="/data/referral_status"/>
			<bind nodeset="/data/health_status_followup"/>
			<bind nodeset="/data/status_unknown" relevant="/data/health_status_followup = '4'"/>
			<bind nodeset="/data/other_comments" type="xsd:string"/>
			<bind nodeset="/data/educ_same_worse" relevant="/data/health_status_followup = '2' or /data/health_status_followup = '3'"/>
			<bind nodeset="/data/educ_importance_hf" relevant="/data/health_status_followup = '2' or /data/health_status_followup = '3'"/>
			<bind nodeset="/data/referral_form" relevant="/data/health_status_followup = '2' or /data/health_status_followup = '3'"/>
			<bind nodeset="/data/new_registration" relevant="/data/health_status_followup = '2' or /data/health_status_followup = '3'"/>
			<bind nodeset="/data/educ_better" relevant="/data/health_status_followup = '1'"/>
			<bind nodeset="/data/educ_followup_again" relevant="/data/status_unknown = '1'"/>
			<bind nodeset="/data/prev_referral_given"/>
			<bind nodeset="/data/new_referral_given" calculate="if(/data/health_status_followup = '2' or /data/health_status_followup = '3' or /data/referral_status = '0', 'yes', 'no')"/>
			<bind nodeset="/data/close_case" calculate="if(/data/health_status_followup = '1' or /data/health_status_followup = '0' or /data/status_unknown = '2' or /data/status_unknown = '3' or /data/status_unknown = '0', 'yes', 'no')"/>
			<itext>
				<translation lang="por" default="">
					<text id="home_visit-label">
						<value>&#201; uma visita domicili&#225;ria?</value>
					</text>
					<text id="home_visit-1-label">
						<value>Sim</value>
					</text>
					<text id="home_visit-0-label">
						<value>N&#226;o</value>
					</text>
					<text id="referral_status-label2">
						<value>Voc&#234; transferiu este paciente para a US durante a sua &#250;tima consulta. O paciente foi para a US?</value>
					</text>
					<text id="referral_status-1-label">
						<value>Sim</value>
					</text>
					<text id="referral_status-0-label">
						<value>N&#227;o</value>
					</text>
					<text id="health_status_followup-label">
						<value>Como o que est&#225; a crian&#231;a?</value>
					</text>
					<text id="health_status-1-label">
						<value>Melhor</value>
					</text>
					<text id="health_status-2-label">
						<value>Mesmo</value>
					</text>
					<text id="health_status-3-label">
						<value>Pior</value>
					</text>
					<text id="health_status-4-label">
						<value>Desconhecido</value>
					</text>
					<text id="health_status-0-label">
						<value>Morte</value>
					</text>
					<text id="status_unknown-label">
						<value>Por que &#233; desconhecido?</value>
					</text>
					<text id="status_unknpwn-1-label">
						<value>N&#227;o est&#225; dispon&#237;vel.</value>
					</text>
					<text id="status_unknpwn-2-label">
						<value>M&#227;e n&#227;o quer que o APE observa a crian&#231;a</value>
					</text>
					<text id="status_unknpwn-3-label">
						<value>O paciente se afastou.</value>
					</text>
					<text id="status_unknpwn-0-label">
						<value>Outro motivo.</value>
					</text>
					<text id="other_comments-label">
						<value>Outros coment&#225;rios:</value>
					</text>
					<text id="educ_same_worse-label">
						<value>A crian&#231;a n&#227;o est&#225; a se sentir melhor. Transferir urgentamente para a US mais pr&#243;xima.</value>
					</text>
					<text id="educ_importance_hf-label">
						<value>Tem alguma dificuldade para levar a sua crian&#231;a &#224; US?   Falar com o seu APE sobre como solucionar o  problema.</value>
					</text>
					<text id="referral_form-label">
						<value>Preencha a guia de refer&#234;ncia e fa&#231;a o seguimento depois de 1 dia.</value>
					</text>
					<text id="new_registration-label">
						<value>Se tem sintomas novas, por favor preencha outro formulario de registro para este bebe.</value>
					</text>
					<text id="educ_better-label">
						<value>Parabens! A crian&#231;a se sente melhor. Aconselhar a mae levar a crian&#231;a ao APE siempre cuanda esta doente.</value>
					</text>
					<text id="educ_followup_again-label">
						<value>Volta a visitar a crian&#231;a depois de 1 dia para dar seguimento.</value>
					</text>
				</translation>
				<translation lang="en">
					<text id="home_visit-label">
						<value>Is it a home visit?</value>
					</text>
					<text id="home_visit-1-label">
						<value>Yes</value>
					</text>
					<text id="home_visit-0-label">
						<value>No</value>
					</text>
					<text id="referral_status-label2">
						<value>You referred this patient to the health facility during your last meeting, did they go?</value>
					</text>
					<text id="referral_status-1-label">
						<value>Yes</value>
					</text>
					<text id="referral_status-0-label">
						<value>No</value>
					</text>
					<text id="health_status_followup-label">
						<value>How is the child?</value>
					</text>
					<text id="health_status-1-label">
						<value>Better</value>
					</text>
					<text id="health_status-2-label">
						<value>Same</value>
					</text>
					<text id="health_status-3-label">
						<value>Worse</value>
					</text>
					<text id="health_status-4-label">
						<value>Unknown</value>
					</text>
					<text id="health_status-0-label">
						<value>Dead</value>
					</text>
					<text id="status_unknown-label">
						<value>Why is it unknown?</value>
					</text>
					<text id="status_unknpwn-1-label">
						<value>Patient not available</value>
					</text>
					<text id="status_unknpwn-2-label">
						<value>Mother doesn't want APE to treat child</value>
					</text>
					<text id="status_unknpwn-3-label">
						<value>Patient has moved</value>
					</text>
					<text id="status_unknpwn-0-label">
						<value>Other reason</value>
					</text>
					<text id="other_comments-label">
						<value>Other comments:</value>
					</text>
					<text id="educ_same_worse-label">
						<value>The child is not feeling better. Transfer immediately to the nearest HF.</value>
					</text>
					<text id="educ_importance_hf-label">
						<value>Do you have any difficulties in getting your child to a US? Talk to your APE about how to address any challenges.</value>
					</text>
					<text id="referral_form-label">
						<value>Fill in the referral form and follow up after 1 day.</value>
					</text>
					<text id="new_registration-label">
						<value>If new symtoms have appeared, please fill out another registration form for this infant.</value>
					</text>
					<text id="educ_better-label">
						<value>Congrats! The child is feeling better. Encourage the mother to take the infant to the APE whenever the child becomes sick.</value>
					</text>
					<text id="educ_followup_again-label">
						<value>Return after 1 day for follow up.</value>
					</text>
				</translation>
			</itext>
		<bind nodeset="/data/case/@date_modified" type="dateTime" calculate="/data/meta/timeEnd"/><bind nodeset="/data/case/@user_id" calculate="/data/meta/userID"/><bind nodeset="/data/case/@case_id" calculate="instance('commcaresession')/session/data/case_id"/><bind nodeset="/data/case/update/referral_given" relevant="count(/data/new_referral_given) &gt; 0" calculate="/data/new_referral_given"/><bind nodeset="/data/case/close" relevant="/data/close_case = 'yes'"/><setvalue ref="/data/prev_referral_given" event="xforms-ready" value="instance('casedb')/casedb/case[@case_id=instance('commcaresession')/session/data/case_id]/referral_given"/><setvalue ref="/data/meta/deviceID" event="xforms-ready" value="instance('commcaresession')/session/context/deviceid"/><setvalue ref="/data/meta/timeStart" event="xforms-ready" value="now()"/><bind nodeset="/data/meta/timeStart" type="xsd:dateTime"/><setvalue ref="/data/meta/timeEnd" event="xforms-revalidate" value="now()"/><bind nodeset="/data/meta/timeEnd" type="xsd:dateTime"/><setvalue ref="/data/meta/username" event="xforms-ready" value="instance('commcaresession')/session/context/username"/><setvalue ref="/data/meta/userID" event="xforms-ready" value="instance('commcaresession')/session/context/userid"/><setvalue ref="/data/meta/instanceID" event="xforms-ready" value="uuid()"/><setvalue ref="/data/meta/appVersion" event="xforms-ready" value="instance('commcaresession')/session/context/appversion"/></model>
	</h:head>
	<h:body>
		<select1 ref="/data/home_visit">
			<label ref="jr:itext('home_visit-label')"/>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('home_visit-1-label')"/>
				<value>1</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('home_visit-0-label')"/>
				<value>0</value>
			</item>
		</select1>
		<select1 ref="/data/referral_status">
			<label ref="jr:itext('referral_status-label2')"/>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('referral_status-1-label')"/>
				<value>1</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('referral_status-0-label')"/>
				<value>0</value>
			</item>
		</select1>
		<select1 ref="/data/health_status_followup">
			<label ref="jr:itext('health_status_followup-label')"/>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('health_status-1-label')"/>
				<value>1</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('health_status-2-label')"/>
				<value>2</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('health_status-3-label')"/>
				<value>3</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('health_status-4-label')"/>
				<value>4</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('health_status-0-label')"/>
				<value>0</value>
			</item>
		</select1>
		<select1 ref="/data/status_unknown">
			<label ref="jr:itext('status_unknown-label')"/>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('status_unknpwn-1-label')"/>
				<value>1</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('status_unknpwn-2-label')"/>
				<value>2</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('status_unknpwn-3-label')"/>
				<value>3</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('status_unknpwn-0-label')"/>
				<value>0</value>
			</item>
		</select1>
		<input ref="/data/other_comments">
			<label ref="jr:itext('other_comments-label')"/>
		</input>
		<trigger ref="/data/educ_same_worse">
			<label ref="jr:itext('educ_same_worse-label')"/>
		</trigger>
		<trigger ref="/data/educ_importance_hf">
			<label ref="jr:itext('educ_importance_hf-label')"/>
		</trigger>
		<trigger ref="/data/referral_form">
			<label ref="jr:itext('referral_form-label')"/>
		</trigger>
		<trigger ref="/data/new_registration">
			<label ref="jr:itext('new_registration-label')"/>
		</trigger>
		<trigger ref="/data/educ_better">
			<label ref="jr:itext('educ_better-label')"/>
		</trigger>
		<trigger ref="/data/educ_followup_again">
			<label ref="jr:itext('educ_followup_again-label')"/>
		</trigger>
	</h:body>
</h:html>